Title: Agent signing is now executed in background job
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: agents
Date: 1591081470
Edition: cee
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

Signing agents in a large Agent Bakery installation can take a long time.
Therefore, the signing process is now performed in a background job, just like
the baking of agent packages.
